WEBVTT

00:09:29.000 --> 00:09:30.656
or get changed in

00:09:30.680 --> 00:09:36.576
supports a lifestyle choice
that you feel offends your morality,

00:09:36.600 --> 00:09:38.200
or your masculinity,

00:09:38.800 --> 00:09:40.256
or your religious beliefs,

00:09:40.280 --> 00:09:42.536
then let me just appeal

00:09:42.560 --> 00:09:46.976
to the part of your heart
that probably, hopefully,

00:09:47.000 --> 00:09:49.680
does care about
the rest of the population.

00:09:51.760 --> 00:09:56.800
If you can't bring yourself
to care enough about people like me,

00:09:57.920 --> 00:10:00.216
then what about women and girls